+## 🔧 Configuration
+
+### **Respectful Scraping Settings:**
+
+Built-in protection for government websites:
+
+```python
+POLITE_DELAY = 2.0  # 2 seconds between requests
+TIMEOUT = 10        # 10 second timeout per request
+MAX_ARTICLES = 5    # Top 5 most recent per source
+
+HEADERS = {
